			<br><br><br>		
			<h2> MOBILE ROBOTIC RESEARCH PLATFORM - WITH A 6-DOF ROBOTIC ARM</h2>
			<p style="text-align:left;margin:3%"> <b>OBJECTIVE</b></p>
			<p style="text-align:justify;margin:3%;margin-left:3%;margin-right:3%;"> The project was to design a mobile robot with a 6-DOF robotic arm mounted on the top. This robot has indoor as well as outdoor applications with an arm for various grasping, picking and other articulate movements. The complete system is to culminate in an intelligent vision powered robot that learns and understands about its environment using a wide range of onboard sensors that form a complete closed loop system. </p>

			<img src="images/swaa/arm.png" style="width:995px;height:521px;margin-left:2%;"></img></p>


			<p style="font-size:22px">SINCE THE COMPANY POLICIES AND <b>NDA</b> don't allow detailed description of the work, so I can mention no more in text. I am open to detailed description, verbally.<p>
